1999", shape=ellipse, URL="RFC2645.html", target="_top", tooltip="This memo proposes a new service, On-Demand Mail Relay (ODMR), which is a profile of SMTP, providing for a secure, extensible, easy to implement approach to the problem. [STANDARDS-TRACK]"];
